.DS_Store
.cursor/
**/.DS_Store
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
terminals/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Safety: this repo is rooted at the home directory.
# Prevent accidentally committing personal/system files.
# We will explicitly add only the Obsidian vault content we care about.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Ignore everything at repo root by default
/*

# Allow gitignore itself
!.gitignore

# Whitelist: Obsidian vault we want to version
!Library/
/Library/*
!Library/Mobile Documents/
/Library/Mobile Documents/*
!Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/
/Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/*
!Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/Documents/
/Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/Documents/*
!Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/Documents/YouTube/
/Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/Documents/YouTube/*
!Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/Documents/YouTube/YouTube/
!Library/Mobile Documents/iCloud~md~obsidian/Documents/YouTube/YouTube/**

# Obsidian: ignore volatile/cache/workspace (keep the rest)
**/.obsidian/cache/
**/.obsidian/workspace.json
**/.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json# Secrets / credentials (never commit)
**/client_secret*.json
**/token.pickle
**/*.pickle
**/.env
**/.env.*
